      <p>SURYA DRISHTI is the interactive front-end of the TAPAS-UHI engine. For this demo, every city is analysed by a <b>deterministic, calibrated synthetic model</b> styled on real ISRO data products and published UHI literature — the same city always returns the same zones and numbers, which is what you want in a live pitch. The full production pipeline (Resourcesat-2 / INSAT-3D / Cartosat-2 ingestion, the PINN energy-balance solver, the GATv2 GNN, and the NSGA-II optimiser) runs separately on live satellite passes; this tool mirrors its method and output shape for instant, judge-facing demonstration.</p>
